ag">Giancarlo Sepe</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/gianluca-martinenghi/" rel="tag">Gianluca Martinenghi</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/gianluca-terranova/" rel="tag">Gianluca terranova</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/irina-lungu/" rel="tag">irina lungu</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/la-traviata/" rel="tag">La Traviata</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/opera-lirica/" rel="tag">Opera lirica</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/stagione-sinfonica-teatro-filarmonico/" rel="tag">Stagione sinfonica teatro filarmonico</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/teatro-filarmonico-di-verona/" rel="tag">teatro filarmonico di Verona</a><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Gabriele Viviani, Giancarlo Sepe, Gianluca Martinenghi, Gianluca terranova, irina lungu, La Traviata, Opera lirica, Stagione sinfonica teatro filarmonico, teatro filarmonico di Verona"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/7a534724d452be116e4581a11b90635f" alt="" /> <img src="http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/7a534724d452be116e4581a11b90635f?s=100&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g" width="100" height="100" alt="" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 photo avatar-default" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Lukas Franceschini"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/lukas/">View all articles by Lukas Franceschini</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text